pageContext.description: Edge blunt and burred. One side of socket is cracked, crushed, and broken.  Decorated with raised lines and dots. Nearly in middle of this specimen is a hole. Sides of this hole are shaped as shown in section.
pageContext.patina: some rich polished patina jade green, this appears to have been partly chipped away. Matte at edge.
